  <h1>Buttress <em><span class="def_type">n.</span> /ˈbətris/</em></h1>
  <p class="lead">A structure built against another structure to support it.</p>

  <hr>
  
  <h3>That's great, what does it do?</h3>
  <p class="lead">Buttress is a collection of popular ruby/rails gems designed for rapid prototyping and application development with the rails 3.2.x framework.  We've put them together and built a bare-bones setup to help get your project prototyped or started.</p>
